# Deposition Tools Ontology
# Industry-general concepts for thin film deposition equipment and processes

@prefix semicont-07-wfe-deposition-tools: <https://semicont.org/ontology/07-wfe/02-deposition-tools#> .
@prefix semicont-shared: <https://semicont.org/ontology/00-shared#> .
